            "title": "日股半日升約1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股造好，重上37000點水平。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數今早高見37326點，半日收報37173點，升354點，升幅0.96%。</p>\n</div>",
