        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段靠穩 恒指回升16點報23616點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段靠穩，恒生指數開市報23616點，升16點或0.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5867點，升22點或0.38%；國企指數以8690點開市，升8點或0.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230810_FI_source-web_9988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230810_FI_source-web_9988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股今早於競價時段個別發展，昨天已逆市報升的阿里巴巴(09988)，今早開報133.8元，回吐0.74%；騰訊(00700)開報513元，升0.2%；美團(03690)開報168.3元，暫時無升跌。滙控(00005)開報85.5元，升0.53%；友邦(01299)開報63.05元，跌1.18%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金川國際(02362)折讓近14%配股；該股今早開報0.66元，跌9.59%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新秀麗(01910)於開市前公布2024年度業績，純利倒退12.9%，每股派息10.74美仙，另料今年首銷售淨額按年錄中低單位數跌幅；該股今早開報19.94元，升2.26%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：新秀麗官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_01910.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：新秀麗官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_01910.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：新秀麗官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">將於今日派成績表的太古(00019)，今早則開報73.4元，升0.27%；同系太古地產(01972)開報16.18元，升0.25%。亦於今日公布業績的九倉(00004)則庂20.35元開市，暫時無升跌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14772495-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%9d%a0%e7%a9%a9-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%8716%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123616%e9%bb%9e",
